lead_paragraph: England striker Jamie Vardy is a "genetic freak" like nine-times Olympic sprint champion Usain Bolt, Leicester City's head of sport science Kevin Paxton said.

headline.print_headline: Vardy Is a 'Genetic Freak' Like Bolt, Says Leicester City Scientist
